name: Symphony Floating Rate Senior Loan Fund
longDescription: Provide monthly distributions, and Preserve capital. The Fund was created to invest in an actively managed, diversified portfolio consisting primarily of short-duration floating rate senior corporate instruments, including senior loans and other senior debt obligations of North American non-investment grade corporate borrowers.
